    "The performance of ChatGPT in identifying suicide and depression suggests a promising future for PLMs for mental health 15, 20, 21.",
    "ChatGPT has presented promising results in the healthcare domain, including applications in healthcare that collect and analyze patients' clinical information including diagnosis, allergies, and details of previous visits.",
